## Orchestrator Integration

This workspace is managed by the parent orchestrator.
- The orchestrator delegates tasks via `query(cwd=this_directory/)`
- Task results must be returned as JSON:
  ```json
  {
    "changed_files": ["changed files"],
    "summary": "work summary",
    "test_result": "pass | fail | skip",
    "downstream_context": "changes affecting other workspaces"
  }
  ```
